					<outline text="3b. Anna Nicole Smith?" created="Tue, 17 Apr 2007 22:26:06 GMT"/>
					<outline text="4. Will anyone notice that while we're venting and emoting about Virginia Tech, hundreds of Iraqis have died." created="Tue, 17 Apr 2007 22:14:59 GMT"/>
