					<outline text="&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.conversationsnetwork.org/podcorps&quot;&gt;PodCorps.org&lt;/a&gt; is a &quot;worldwide army of audio and video stringers who volunteer to record important spoken-word events.&quot;" created="Mon, 16 Apr 2007 15:44:00 GMT"/>
					<outline text="&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.ustream.tv/watch/channel/n6m2nBTlCbmJHPL0,I51JQ&quot;&gt;Watch Scoble drive&lt;/a&gt; to San Francisco. He's listening to the radio, talking on the phone. " created="Mon, 16 Apr 2007 16:02:36 GMT"/>
