					<outline text="I'm featured on the &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.flickr.com/photos/scriptingnews/447874780/&quot;&gt;cover of Wired&lt;/a&gt; next month in a special issue celebrating 10 years of blogging. Many of you were interviewed for this issue, so congrats! &quot;;-&gt;&quot;" created="Fri, 06 Apr 2007 03:06:14 GMT"/>
