				<outline text="Yo Wes!" created="Tue, 03 Apr 2007 01:21:34 GMT" type="outline">
					<outline text="&lt;a href=&quot;http://wmf.editthispage.com/2007/04/02&quot;&gt;Wes Felter checks in&lt;/a&gt;. He &lt;i&gt;was&lt;/i&gt; there at the beginning, and I share his feelings about how code formed blogging, when it should have been the other way around. Oh well. " created="Tue, 03 Apr 2007 01:20:52 GMT"/>
